  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Delete Redemption Schedules</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loiof417da531198434de10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Delete Redemption Schedules </h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> You can use this function to delete redemption schedules you no longer require.\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Features\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Features</h2>\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Selection</span>\n</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper tablenoborder\"><table summary=\"\" class=\"table\" frame=\"border\" border=\"1\" rules=\"all\"><colgroup><col width=\"50%\"><col width=\"50%\"></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\"><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> General Selections</span>\n</p></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> ID number\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> Product type\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> Redemption schedule set\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> Redemption schedule set class\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Redemption Schedule Data</span>\n</p></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> Effective from\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> Entered on\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> Entered by\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> Last edited on\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> Last changed by\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> Redemption schedule\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> First redemption date\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> Redemption schedule file\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> No. of redemptions\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Output</span>\n</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper tablenoborder\"><table summary=\"\" class=\"table\" frame=\"border\" border=\"1\" rules=\"all\"><colgroup><col width=\"50%\"><col width=\"50%\"></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\"><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Output Control</span>\n</p></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> Test run\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> If you set this indicator, the system only performs a test run, and no redemption schedules are deleted.\n</p></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> Display redemption schedules\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> If this indicator is set, the display log contains all the selected redemption schedules that were deleted in the update run. This field is set as a default.\n</p></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> Layout\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> If you have saved a layout, you can select it in this field. The list is then structured in the way you want from the outset.\n</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Activities\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Activities</h2>\n<ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Call up the function and enter selection criteria to ensure that the system only selects the redemption schedules you want to delete.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> First carry out a test run.\n</p><ol class=\"ol\" type=\"a\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> a. Do this by setting the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Test Run</span> indicator.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> b. Also make sure that the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Display Redemption Schedules</span> indicator is set.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> c. If you want to use your own display variant, choose the required layout.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> d. Execute the report.\n</p><p class=\"p\"> The log tells you the number of redemption schedules selected. These are shown in the list.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> e. Check the redemption schedules selected.\n</p><p class=\"p\"> If these are the correct redemption schedules, you can now start the update run. If the list contains redemption schedules that you do not want to delete, check your selection conditions. When you have corrected the selection conditions, carry out another test run.\n</p></li></ol></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Deactivate the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Test Run</span> indicator and perform the update run.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> The system deletes the selected redemption schedules.\n</p></li></ol>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}